import './global.css'
import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

import Dashboard from './Pages/Dashboard.js'
import Theme from './Context/ThemeContext'

const App = () => (
  <Theme>
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Routes>
        <Route path='' element={ <Dashboard /> } />
      </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  </Theme>
)

export default App
